		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Uforce emulation</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was wondering how difficult it would be to emulate the Uforce accessory, a motion dectector device that uses infrared sensors.  While no released games required use of the Uforce, I recently recieved a prototype of Uforce Power Games, an unreleased title that can't be played without it.  I've dumped the rom and would really like to see it supported in emulators one of these days.  Would this be easy to incorporate in emulators?  Impossible?  I'd love to hear any feedback you all might have.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
